lead_paragraph: Trump Entertainment Resorts says it is closing its newest hotel tower and is no longer issuing credit as it prepares for a Dec. 12 shutdown of the Taj Mahal, its lone remaining casino.

headline.main: Taj Mahal Casino Closes Hotel Tower, Ends Credit
